<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM2.3">
<l>kuṇṭu nīruṟai kōḷa rīmata yāṉai kōḷviṭut tāyuṉṉaik</l>
<l>kaṇṭu māluṟu vōṅka ḷaikkaṭaik kaṇka ḷāliṭṭu vātiyēl</l>
<l>vaṇṭa ṉuṇmaṇaṟ ṟeḷḷi yāmvaḷaik kaikaḷāṟ ciramap paṭṭōm</l>
<l>teṇṭi raikkaṭaṟ paḷḷiyā yeṅkaḷ ciṟṟil vantu citaiyēlē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O mighty Lion who reside in the deep ocean! O You who liberated the rutting</l>
<l rend="indent">elephant from [being] killed!</l>
<l>Do not torment us, who experience love at seeing You, with [Your] sideglances!</l>
<l>We exerted ourselves with our braceleted hands, sprinkling fine sand from the mire.</l>
<l>O You whose bed is the ocean with clear waves! Do not come and trample down</l>
<l rend="indent">our small [sand] house!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
